        "explanation": "The matrix is $2I$. The inverse of $kI$ is $(1/k)I = \\begin{bmatrix} 0.5 & 0 \\\\ 0 & 0.5 \\end{bmatrix}$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the determinant of $\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 2 & 4 \\end{bmatrix}$.",
