        "explanation": "$s = (5+6+7)/2 = 9$. Area $= \\sqrt{9(9-5)(9-6)(9-7)} = \\sqrt{9 \\cdot 4 \\cdot 3 \\cdot 2} = \\sqrt{216} = 6\\sqrt{6}$."
      },
      {
